# Frontend Conventions

- Keep route definitions under `frontend/src/routes/`.
- Keep API calls in `frontend/src/services/` and avoid hardcoded URLs.
- Keep request and response shapes in `frontend/src/types/`.
- Keep MSW handlers and Cypress specs aligned with backend contracts.
- Prefer shared UI primitives from `frontend/src/components/ui/`.
- Use environment variables through `VITE_*` configuration.

